HEADWORD: Craving
<hw>Crav"ing</hw> <pr>(-?ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Vehement or urgent
desire; longing for; beseeching.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A succession of <qex>cravings</qex> and satiety.</q>
<rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Crav"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Crav"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Craw</ent>⟦br⟧
